definitions.definition: An alkaloid , C 8 H 10 N 4 O 2 , found naturally in tea and coffee plants, which acts as a mild stimulant on the central nervous system .

main_definition: An alkaloid , C 8 H 10 N 4 O 2 , found naturally in tea and coffee plants, which acts as a mild stimulant on the central nervous system . [from 1830]
